cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual tracking and leverages deep features via off-the-shelf CNN models. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a knowledge distillation framework to compress and transfer CNN models. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of visual tracking algorithms. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with tracking objects in videos. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with real-time tracking which can be useful in robotics applications.
